            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p>\n<p>Boil a kettle</p>\n<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a generous drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p>\n<p>Once hot, add the <strong>diced chicken breast</strong> and cook for 3-4 min or until starting to brown</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2242-Step-2-x200.jpg",
