            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2242-Step-2-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add the <strong>medium egg noodles</strong> to a pot with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cover with<strong> boiled water</strong> until fully submerged</p>\n<p>Bring to the boil over a high heat and cook for 5-6 min or until cooked with a slight bite</p>\n<p>Once done, drain the noodles, reserving a cup of the starchy noodle water</p>",
      "order": 3,
