      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>black bean sauce</strong> to the pan and cook for 1 min further or until the sauce has warmed through and the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!)</p>\n<p>Note: Please make sure you cook your chicken thoroughly (until there’s no pink meat and it’s piping hot!) as cooking equipment varies</p>",
