    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the noodles are done, stir them through the <strong>black bean sauce </strong>– this is your <strong>chicken &amp; black bean noodle stir fry</strong></p>\n<p>Tip: Add a splash of starchy noodle water if your sauce is looking a little dry</p>",
