    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the<strong> chicken &amp; black bean noodle stir fry</strong> in bowls</p>\n<p>Garnish with the<strong> toasted sesame seeds</strong> and <strong>sliced spring onion</strong></p>\n<p>Enjoy!</p>",
